data.description: This is it! Immaculate 3 Bedroom 2 Bath home Built in 2019. This Home Looks brand new and it’s move in ready!  Come see this beautiful house in the centrally located tranquil neighborhood of Sherman Hills.  This home has it all with gorgeous open floor plan huge upgraded fenced in back yard with large vinyl 6X8 fence panels around entire backyard. The house is meticulously maintained with a gorgeous entryway foyer leading you into the spacious great room with an open living room, kitchen, and dining area concept. The master bedroom is nothing short of amazing with its large welcoming space perfect for a grand bed and/or lots of furniture. Lose yourself in this grand Master Bedroom Retreat with lots of natural lighting. . The en-suite is fantastic with a vanity area, shower tub combo, a dressing space and a Huge Walk In Closet. The kitchen has stainless steel double sink, an island bar, microwave, refrigerator, and closet pantry. The kitchen, dining area/ living room areas are perfect for entertaining guests. The split plan features two bedrooms just off the foyer.  Bedroom 2 and Bedroom 3 are both spacious and have nice closets for your clothes and /or storage.  The second bathroom has a shower tub combo and a stately vanity with dark cabinetry.  There is a covered porch in the back, perfect for relaxing and enjoying the afternoon.  Easy access to I-75 for those quick trips to Tampa or north to Gainesville or Ocala.  Restaurants and grocery store are close or visit nearby Brooksville or Dade City. Home is NOT in a flood zone no flood insurance required.  Make an appointment and Come see your new home located in the Sherman Hills Golf Community.
